<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 10:07:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>成千上万的乌克兰人在寻找失踪亲人时生活在痛苦和不确定之中</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/thousands-of-ukrainians-in-agony-as-they-search-for-missing-loved-ones/articleshow/107940582.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107940582.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于俄罗斯的入侵，乌克兰有数千人失踪。家人拼命寻找亲人，但缺乏官方信息让他们陷入困境。红十字国际委员会收集 DNA 样本以确定失踪人员的身份。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 09:24:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/thousands-of-ukrainians-in-agony-as-they-search-for-missing-loved-ones/articleshow/107940582.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦最高法院在强烈反对后捍卫对少数群体的裁决</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-supreme-court-defends-ruling-on-minorities-after-backlash/articleshow/107940868.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107940868.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦最高法院为首席大法官卡齐·法兹·伊萨（Qazi Faez Isa）辩护，此前他因一项涉及亵渎罪的裁决而面临强烈反对和死亡威胁。这项裁决涉及释放艾哈迈迪教派的一名男子，该教派被一些强硬的穆斯林学者认为是异端。该男子被指控分享了一段被禁止的艾哈迈迪文本，这被视为亵渎。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 09:36:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-supreme-court-defends-ruling-on-minorities-after-backlash/articleshow/107940868.cms</guid></item><item><title>警方称瑞典约有 62,000 人与犯罪团伙有关联</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/62000-persons-linked-to-criminal-gangs-in-sweden-police/articleshow/107940485.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107940485.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;瑞典约有 62,000 人活跃于犯罪网络或与犯罪网络有联系。过去十年，致命枪击事件增加了两倍多。 2022年，瑞典发生了62起致命枪击事件，是挪威、丹麦和芬兰三国枪击事件总和的九倍。爆炸袭击也创历史新高。 2021 年 9 月是瑞典自 2019 年以来死亡人数最多的一个月。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 09:22:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/62000-persons-linked-to-criminal-gangs-in-sweden-police/articleshow/107940485.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列对最大买家印度的军品出口未受加沙战争影响</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/israels-military-exports-to-top-buyer-india-unaffected-by-gaza-war/articleshow/107940247.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107940247.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 09:11:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/israels-military-exports-to-top-buyer-india-unaffected-by-gaza-war/articleshow/107940247.cms</guid></item><item><title>奥地利前总理塞巴斯蒂安·库尔茨伪证案审判进入最后一天</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/austrian-ex-chancellor-sebastian-kurzs-perjury-trial-enters-final-day/articleshow/107940014.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107940014.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;奥地利前总理塞巴斯蒂安·库尔茨的伪证案审判即将结束。检察官指控他淡化了自己对 OBAG 任命的影响力。库尔兹否认有不当行为。他的政治前途和声誉受到威胁。公众舆论反对他重返领导岗位。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 09:02:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/austrian-ex-chancellor-sebastian-kurzs-perjury-trial-enters-final-day/articleshow/107940014.cms</guid></item><item><title>弗拉基米尔·普京称俄罗斯95%的核力量已实现现代化</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/vladimir-putin-says-95-of-russias-nuclear-forces-have-been-modernised/articleshow/107939248.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107939248.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 08:41:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/vladimir-putin-says-95-of-russias-nuclear-forces-have-been-modernised/articleshow/107939248.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列总理内塔尼亚胡公布了战后加沙计划的细节</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-pm-netanyahus-plan-for-postwar-gaza-security-control-and-civilian-affairs/articleshow/107938169.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107938169.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 08:07:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-pm-netanyahus-plan-for-postwar-gaza-security-control-and-civilian-affairs/articleshow/107938169.cms</guid></item><item><title>韩国医院延长工作时间应对医生抗议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korean-hospitals-extend-working-hours-to-tackle-doctors-protest/articleshow/107938029.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107938029.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 08:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korean-hospitals-extend-working-hours-to-tackle-doctors-protest/articleshow/107938029.cms</guid></item><item><title>受乌克兰鼓舞，俄罗斯庆祝爱国节日</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-marks-patriotic-holiday-amid-ukraine-offensive/articleshow/107936009.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107936009.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;总统弗拉基米尔·普京在进攻两周年前夕赞扬了乌克兰的战士，承认他们为对抗弹药短缺的乌克兰军队所做的努力。普京的讲话是在莫斯科的“祖国保卫者日”爱国节日期间发表的，这个节日传统上展示了军事盛况和克里姆林宫支持的爱国主义。本周早些时候，他嘲笑乌克兰士兵从阿夫季夫卡“混乱地逃亡”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 07:03:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-marks-patriotic-holiday-amid-ukraine-offensive/articleshow/107936009.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普承诺捍卫基督教，反对左派，他说左派想要“推倒十字架”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-vows-to-protect-christianity-against-the-lefts-attempt-to-tear-down-crosses/articleshow/107935007.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107935007.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普在宗教广播公司大会上发表讲话时承诺保护基督教价值观，并警告左翼人士希望“拆除十字架”。他还表达了捍卫基督教信仰及其象征的承诺。特朗普在共和党初选中受到青睐，曾经拥挤的竞选场地现在只剩下他和他的前驻联合国大使尼基·黑利(Nikki Haley)。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 06:36:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-vows-to-protect-christianity-against-the-lefts-attempt-to-tear-down-crosses/articleshow/107935007.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国高速公路结冰 百车连环连环相撞 多人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/several-injured-in-100-car-pile-up-on-icy-china-expressway/articleshow/107936768.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107936768.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;因极端天气条件，苏州高速公路结冰，100多辆汽车相撞，多人受伤入院治疗。官方媒体、中央电视台和社交媒体的视频显示，汽车成群结队，玻璃和碎片散落各处。事故原因正在调查中。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 07:24:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/several-injured-in-100-car-pile-up-on-icy-china-expressway/articleshow/107936768.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰两年的战争改变了军队的思维方式</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/two-years-of-war-in-ukraine-has-changed-the-way-militaries-think/articleshow/107934045.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107934045.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;弗拉基米尔·普京对乌克兰的入侵彻底改变了战争，普及了无人机并暴露了供应链独立的重要性。无人机在压倒坦克等大型军事资产方面的敏捷性和有效性，以及它们瞄准部队和扰乱敌方行动的能力，已经重塑了战争战略。这场战争导致了一个更加两极化的世界，并凸显了欧洲增加军费开支的必要性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 06:12:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/two-years-of-war-in-ukraine-has-changed-the-way-militaries-think/articleshow/107934045.cms</guid></item><item><title>乔·拜登的狗指挥官咬了特工至少 24 次</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/joe-bidens-dog-commander-bit-secret-service-agents-at-least-24-times/articleshow/107934051.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107934051.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 06:12:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/joe-bidens-dog-commander-bit-secret-service-agents-at-least-24-times/articleshow/107934051.cms</guid></item><item><title>“穿越圣地亚哥边境的中国移民比墨西哥人还要多”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/more-chinese-migrants-are-crossing-san-diego-border-than-mexicans/articleshow/107933537.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107933537.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国公民是圣地亚哥边境的第二大移民群体，仅次于哥伦比亚人，自 10 月份以来已遇到 21,000 人次。一份新报告显示，自2021财年以来，中国寻求庇护者人数猛增，近几个月超过了墨西哥人数。美国海关和边境保护局的数据显示，自本财年开始以来，圣地亚哥地区有 21,000 名中国公民，而墨西哥人和 28,000 名哥伦比亚人则为 18,700 名。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 06:06:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/more-chinese-migrants-are-crossing-san-diego-border-than-mexicans/articleshow/107933537.cms</guid></item><item><title>韩国健康警报因医生罢工而升级为“严重”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korea-raises-health-alert-to-severe-as-doctors-walkout/articleshow/107933029.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107933029.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于见习医生大规模罢工，抗议政府招收更多医学院学生的计划，韩国将健康警报提升至最高级别。公立医院将延长工作时间、拒绝病人、取消手术，急诊室、重症监护室和手术室也将面临混乱。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 05:30:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korea-raises-health-alert-to-severe-as-doctors-walkout/articleshow/107933029.cms</guid></item><item><title>军方称俄罗斯无人机袭击乌克兰敖德萨造成一人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-drone-strike-in-ukraines-odessa-kills-one-military-says/articleshow/107931670.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107931670.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一架俄罗斯无人机袭击了乌克兰黑海港口敖德萨的商业区，造成一人死亡并引发火灾。消防队员找到了一具尸体，救援队正在努力控制火势。还使用了导弹，但未能击中目标。九架无人机被拦截。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 04:42:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-drone-strike-in-ukraines-odessa-kills-one-military-says/articleshow/107931670.cms</guid></item><item><title>“阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼的遗产将继续下去”：美国总统拜登会见已故俄罗斯领导人的妻子和女儿</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-president-biden-meets-dead-russian-leaders-wife-daughter/articleshow/107932123.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107932123.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 05:09:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-president-biden-meets-dead-russian-leaders-wife-daughter/articleshow/107932123.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿拉巴马州法院对试管婴儿的裁决被拜登称为“令人愤慨和不可接受”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/alabama-supreme-court-ruling-on-ivf-outrageous-and-unacceptable-biden/articleshow/107930775.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107930775.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 04:04:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/alabama-supreme-court-ruling-on-ivf-outrageous-and-unacceptable-biden/articleshow/107930775.cms</guid></item><item><title>“官员在宴席上撒盐，以遏制中国的过度消费”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/officials-pour-salt-on-feast-to-curb-excessive-spending-in-china/articleshow/107930795.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107930795.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国地方政府官员在一次乡村宴会上为婴儿第一次理发举行“剃发庆祝活动”时，在食物上撒盐，引发争议。该事件涉及贵州省小海镇的官员。威宁县政府发表声明，对他们的行为表示歉意。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 04:10:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/officials-pour-salt-on-feast-to-curb-excessive-spending-in-china/articleshow/107930795.cms</guid></item><item><title>西班牙：火灾吞没巴伦西亚的高层公寓楼</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/fire-engulfs-high-rise-apartment-block-in-valencia/articleshow/107930717.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107930717.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;西班牙巴伦西亚一栋公寓楼发生火灾，造成 4 人死亡、13 人受伤。大火从四楼开始，迅速蔓延到整栋大楼。居民被困在阳台上等待救援。受伤者包括一名儿童和六名消防员。当局出动了 22 支消防队和 5 辆救护车，并在现场设立了一家野战医院。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 04:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/fire-engulfs-high-rise-apartment-block-in-valencia/articleshow/107930717.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>